    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years! Whether you\u2019re commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is super reliable and ready for its next adventure. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
