      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid condition and has plenty of life left for its next adventure. I\u2019ve really looked after this car, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road whenever you are. It's a smooth, reliable drive that won't let you down. I'd love for it to go to a great home\u2014feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis maintains its composure with a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a recently inspected rear subframe. Maintenance is up to date, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and valve clearance adjustment. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain sharp. Riding on staggered alloys with high-performance rubber, this M3 offers an authentic analog driving experience with the structural rigidity and damping profile expected of a well-cared-for enthusiast machine.",
